sticker-2283.name: Sticker | apEX | Krakow 2017
sticker-2283.description:
This item commemorates the 2017 PGL Krakow CS:GO Championship.

This sticker can be applied to any weapon you own and can be scraped to look more worn. You can scrape the same sticker multiple times, making it a bit more worn each time, until it is removed from the weapon.

This sticker was autographed by professional player Dan Madesclaire playing for G2 Esports at Krakow 2017.\n\n50% of the proceeds from the sale of this sticker support the included players and organizations.

This sticker can be applied to any weapon you own and can be scraped to look more worn. You can scrape the same sticker multiple times, making it a bit more worn each time, until it is removed from the weapon.

This sticker was autographed by professional player Miikka Kemppi playing for PENTA Sports at Krakow 2017.\n\n50% of the proceeds from the sale of this sticker support the included players and organizations.
